{"parse":{"title":"Faith School Menace?","pageid":28472389,"revid":797464362,"text":{"*":"<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\">\n</p>\n<table class=\"infobox vevent\" style=\"width:22em\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" class=\"summary\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-style: italic; background: #CCCCFF; padding: 0.25em 1em; line-height: 1.5em;\">Faith School Menace?</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Written by</th><td>\n<a href=\"/wiki/Richard_Dawkins\" title=\"Richard Dawkins\">Richard Dawkins</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Directed by</th><td class=\"attendee\">\nMolly Milton</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Country of origin</th><td>\nUK</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Original <span class=\"nowrap\">language(s)</span></th><td>\nEnglish</td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" class=\"summary\" style=\"text-align:center;background: #CCCCFF; padding: 0.25em 1em; line-height: 1.5em;\">Production</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\"><span class=\"nowrap\">Producer(s)</span></th><td>\n<a href=\"/wiki/Russell_Barnes\" title=\"Russell Barnes\">Russell Barnes</a></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" class=\"summary\" style=\"text-align:center;background: #CCCCFF; padding: 0.25em 1em; line-height: 1.5em;\">Release</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Original release</th><td>\n18 August 2010</td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" class=\"summary\" style=\"text-align:center;background: #CCCCFF; padding: 0.25em 1em; line-height: 1.5em;\">Chronology</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Preceded by</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/wiki/The_Genius_of_Charles_Darwin\" title=\"The Genius of Charles Darwin\">The Genius of Charles Darwin</a></i></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><i><b>Faith School Menace?</b></i> is a television documentary presented by <a href=\"/wiki/Richard_Dawkins\" title=\"Richard Dawkins\">Richard Dawkins</a> which explores the effects of <a href=\"/wiki/Faith_school\" title=\"Faith school\">faith schools</a> on the students in them and society in general by taking examples in particular from UK faith schools, with the stated aim <i>\"to explore the balance of rights between a parent's right to educate a child in their own faith, and the children's rights to determine their own beliefs and approach the world with a genuinely open mind\"</i>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Scotsman_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Scotsman-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>At the time of broadcast, one third of British schools had some kind of religious affiliation.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Scotsman_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Scotsman-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>  Dawkins was refused entry to <a href=\"/wiki/Catholic_school\" title=\"Catholic school\">Catholic</a> and <a href=\"/wiki/Jewish_day_school\" title=\"Jewish day school\">Jewish</a> faith schools, but was allowed to film in a <a href=\"/wiki/Muslim_school\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Muslim school\">Muslim school</a>, where children were taught what the theory of <a href=\"/wiki/Evolution\" title=\"Evolution\">evolution</a> was, but that it was not true.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Indy_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Indy-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>It was first aired on <a href=\"/wiki/More4\" title=\"More4\">More4</a> on 18 August 2010.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Faith_School_Menace%3F&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"reflist\" style=\"list-style-type: decimal;\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Scotsman-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">^ <a href=\"#cite_ref-Scotsman_1-0\"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href=\"#cite_ref-Scotsman_1-1\"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation news\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.scotsman.com/news/tv-review-faith-schools-menace-1-821648\">\"TV review: Faith Schools Menace?\"</a>. <i><a href=\"/wiki/The_Scotsman\" title=\"The Scotsman\">The Scotsman</a></i>. 19 August 2010.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=The+Scotsman&amp;rft.atitle=TV+review%3A+Faith+Schools+Menace%3F&amp;rft.date=2010-08-19&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.scotsman.com%2Fnews%2Ftv-review-faith-schools-menace-1-821648&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AFaith+School+Menace%3F\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Indy-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-Indy_2-0\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation news\">Sutcliffe, Tom (19 August 2010). <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/tv/reviews/last-nights-tv-faith-schools-menacemore-4-2056104.html\">\"Last Night's TV: Faith Schools Menace?/More 4\"</a>. <i><a href=\"/wiki/The_Independent\" title=\"The Independent\">The Independent</a></i>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=The+Independent&amp;rft.atitle=Last+Night%27s+TV%3A+Faith+Schools+Menace%3F%2FMore+4&amp;rft.date=2010-08-19&amp;rft.aulast=Sutcliffe&amp;rft.aufirst=Tom&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.independent.co.uk%2Farts-entertainment%2Ftv%2Freviews%2Flast-nights-tv-faith-schools-menacemore-4-2056104.html&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AFaith+School+Menace%3F\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_links\">External links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.